      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "蔡邕上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "闲庭——",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "一枝花",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "槐影转，深院荷香满，帘垂清昼永，怎消遣？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "翠竹影摇金，水殿帘栊映碧阴。人静昼长无外事，沉吟，碧酒金樽懒去斟。幽恨苦相寻，离别经年没音信。寒暑相催人易老，关心，欲把闲愁付玉琴。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "吓，琴、鹤二童。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "啥个？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "在象牙床上取蕉尾纨扇出来！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "来哉！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "琴童、鹤童同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同金钱花",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "自小承值书房、书房，快活其实难当、难当，只管打扇与烧香，荷亭畔好乘凉，吃饱饭上眠床。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "老爷，蕉尾纨扇有了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "放下。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "是哉！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "你二人一个烧香，一个打扇，违者各打十三。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "懒画眉",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "强对南熏奏虞弦，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童"
      ],
      "text": "兄弟你烧香，我打扇。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "有理个。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "懒画眉",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "只觉指下馀音不似前。那些个流水共高山，只见满眼风波恶，似离别当年怀水仙。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "环佩声响，夫人出堂。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "尔等回避。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童"
      ],
      "text": "是哉！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "琴童、鹤童同下，牛氏上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
