      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "久闻相公善于音律，如何来到此间，丝竹之音杳然绝响？奴家斗胆，请教相公试操一曲如何？",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "吖，夫人要听琴么？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "弹什么好？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "当此清凉夏景，弹一曲风入松罢。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "使得。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "琴曲",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "一别家乡远，思亲泪暗弹。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "相公弹差了。风入松为何弹起思归引来？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "吓，夫人，下官在家惯弹旧弦，这新弦欲弹不惯。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "何不撇了新弦，重整旧弦？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "新旧二弦俱撇不下！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "既撇不下，提它怎么？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "吓夫人！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "相公。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "危弦已断，新弦不惯。旧弦再上不能，待撇了新弦难拚。我一弹再鼓，我一弹再鼓，又被宫商错乱。非干心变，这般好凉天，正是此曲才堪听，又被风吹别调间。",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "相公！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "非弹不惯，只是你意慵心懒。既道是寡鹄孤鸾，又道是昭君宫怨。更思归别鹤，无非愁叹，有何难见？即不然，你道是除了知音听，道奴不是知音不与弹！",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "琴童、鹤童、惜春同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同烧夜香",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "楼台倒影入池塘，绿树阴浓夏正长，一架蔷薇满院香。泛霞觞，卷起帘儿，明月正上。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕",
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "看酒。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "有酒。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021462023-10-05",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕",
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "新篁池阁，",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "槐阴庭院，日永红尘隔断。碧栏杆外，寒飞漱玉清泉。只觉香肌无暑，素质生风，小簟琅玕展。昼长人困也，好清闲。忽被棋声惊昼眠。金缕唱，碧筒劝，向冰山雪巘排佳宴，清世界有几人见？",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "蔷薇帘箔，荷花池馆，一点风来香满。湘帘日永，香销宝篆沉烟。漫有枕欹寒玉，扇动齐纨，怎遂得黄香愿？",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "相公为何落下泪来？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "非也。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "我猛然心地热，不觉透香汗，",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "惜春，纨扇。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "我欲向南窗一醉眠。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "金缕唱，碧筒劝，向冰山雪巘排佳宴，清世界有几人见？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖节节高〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕",
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "向晚来雨过南轩，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同梁州新郎",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "见池面红妆零乱。渐轻雷隐隐雨收云散。但闻得荷香十里，新月一钩，此景佳无限。兰汤初浴罢，不觉晚妆残，深院黄昏懒去眠。金缕唱，碧筒劝，向冰山雪巘排佳宴，清世界有几人见？",
      "text_length": 82
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖庆南枝〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同节节高",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕",
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "涟漪戏彩鸳，把露荷翻，清香泻下琼珠溅。香风扇，芳沼边，闲亭畔，坐来不觉人清健，蓬莱阆苑何足羡。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021462023-10-05",
      "text_length": 96
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同节节高",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "只恐西风又惊秋，暗中不觉流年换。清宵思爽然，好凉天，瑶台月下清虚殿。神仙眷，开玳筳，重欢宴，任教玉漏催银箭，水晶宫里把笙歌按。只恐西风又惊秋，暗中不觉流年换。",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "光阴迅速如飞电，好良宵可惜渐阑，管取欢娱歌声喧。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00066",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "蔡邕"
      ],
      "text": "几鼓了？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00067",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "琴童",
        "鹤童",
        "惜春"
      ],
      "text": "三鼓了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00068",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "相公。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00069",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "牛氏"
      ],
      "text": "欢娱休问夜如何，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902146_e00070",
      "play_id": "70902146",
      "scene_id": "70902146_s01",
